My adult kids STILL love the Pee Wee movies.

I know you are, but what am I? I have missed Pee-Wee! My 8 year old son found Pee-Wee's playhouse on Netflix and started watching the series. He loves it! So naturally, I had to get him the ultimate Pee-Wee movie (Pee-Wee's Big Adventure). I loved the feeling of nostalgia while watching this. It's such a great movie. (the table-top dance scene is running through my mind as I write this, lol)

Don't get me wrong, Big Top is a Pee-Wee classic too, but Big Adventure takes the cake. It's a carefree movie packed with silliness and laughs.

Plus, you get 2 movies in 1 - you can't beat that!
We will be watching this DVD for years to come.

I purchased this dvd for my  Grandson, Nathaniel.  He loves Big Top Pee Wee and Pee Wee's  Big Adventure.  Both of his movies were old and scratched from lots of watching.  I gave Nathaniel his present to open and his little face was so adorable when he saw he had both movies in one.  He loved this one gift so much, he carried it the bathroom with him to keep it safe.  I laughed and loved the fact I had made him so happy.  Pee Wee Herman movies are a treasure to Nathaniel and I am sure he thought someone might try to snatch it.  This purchase and my grandson's face made this a very special experience...
